frontmatter.text: The tagline should inspire confidence and interest, focusing on the value that your overall approach offers to your audience. Use a heading typeface and keep your tagline to just a few words, and donâ€™t confuse or mystify. Use the right side of the grid to explain the tagline a bit more. What are your goals?
